<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Client Agreement</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111827;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .doc-subtitle strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .parties-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .party-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .party-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .party-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .party-details {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .clause {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .clause h4 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .clause p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .clause ul,
        .clause ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .clause li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .scope-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .scope-table th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            width: 35%;
        }

        .scope-table td {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .important-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .important-box h4 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .important-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .sig-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .sig-field {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .sig-field-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sig-field-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="doc-title">Client Agreement</div>
        <div class="doc-subtitle"><strong>Agreement Date:</strong> {{effectiveDate}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Agreement
                No:</strong> {{#if agreementNumber}}{{agreementNumber}}{{else}}CA-2024-001{{/if}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="parties-grid">
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Service Provider</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="party-details">{{{companyAddress}}}{{#if companyEmail}}<br>{{companyEmail}}{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Client</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{clientName}}</div>
            <div class="party-details">{{{clientAddress}}}{{#if clientEmail}}<br>{{clientEmail}}{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>This Client Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into as of <strong>{{effectiveDate}}</strong> between the
            parties identified above. This Agreement governs the business relationship and sets forth the terms under
            which the Service Provider shall deliver services to the Client.</p>

        <table class="scope-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Project/Service</th>
                <td>{{{serviceDescription}}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Start Date</th>
                <td>{{effectiveDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Duration</th>
                <td>{{#if duration}}{{duration}}{{else}}12 months{{/if}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Total Value</th>
                <td>₹{{totalAmount}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Payment Terms</th>
                <td>{{#if paymentTerms}}{{paymentTerms}}{{else}}Net 30 days{{/if}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>1. Scope of Engagement</h4>
            <p>The Service Provider shall provide the services described above in accordance with the specifications
                mutually agreed upon. Any changes to the scope must be documented through a written change order signed
                by both parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>2. Client Responsibilities</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide timely access to information, personnel, and resources necessary for service delivery.</li>
                <li>Designate a primary point of contact for all project communications.</li>
                <li>Review and provide feedback on deliverables within {{#if reviewPeriod}}{{reviewPeriod}}{{else}}5
                    business days{{/if}}.</li>
                <li>Make payments in accordance with the agreed payment schedule.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>3. Payment Terms</h4>
            <p>The Client agrees to pay the Service Provider ₹{{totalAmount}} as per the agreed payment schedule.
                Invoices are due within {{#if paymentTerms}}{{paymentTerms}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}} of receipt. Late
                payments shall attract interest at 1.5% per month.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>4. Confidentiality</h4>
            <p>Both parties agree to maintain strict confidentiality regarding all proprietary information, trade
                secrets, and business data shared during the course of this engagement. This obligation survives
                termination of this Agreement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>5. Intellectual Property</h4>
            <p>All deliverables created specifically for the Client under this Agreement shall become the property of
                the Client upon full payment. The Service Provider retains rights to pre-existing intellectual property,
                tools, and methodologies used in delivering services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>6. Termination</h4>
            <p>Either party may terminate this Agreement with {{#if noticePeriod}}{{noticePeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}}
                written notice. In the event of termination, the Client shall pay for all services and work completed up
                to the effective date of termination.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>7. Limitation of Liability</h4>
            <p>The Service Provider's total liability shall not exceed the total fees paid under this Agreement. Neither
                party shall be liable for indirect, special, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="important-box">
            <h4>Dispute Resolution</h4>
            <p>Any disputes shall first be resolved through good faith negotiation. If unresolved within 30 days, the
                dispute shall be submitted to binding arbitration under the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996, with
                the seat in {{#if jurisdiction}}{{jurisdiction}}{{else}}Bangalore, India{{/if}}.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>8. Governing Law</h4>
            <p>This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. The courts of
                {{#if jurisdiction}}{{jurisdiction}}{{else}}Bangalore{{/if}} shall have exclusive jurisdiction.</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF,</strong> the parties have executed this Client Agreement as of the date first
            written above.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-card">
            <div class="sig-title">Service Provider</div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Name & Title</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig-card">
            <div class="sig-title">Client</div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Name: {{clientName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{companyName}} — Client Agreement</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>